Subject: EPP Appliance is running low Disk Space | Infibeam Avenues Limited
Description: One of customer (Infibeam Avenues Limited) is facing issue with EPP Appliance is running on low disk space and they need to free-up the space.
What_We_Know__c: The customer system partition is running on low disk space.  We still need to have a remote session in order to investigate further.
Next_Steps__c: We need to have a remote session in order to investigate further.
Solution_Comment__c: Solved by clearing the SIEM logs which were not sent to their SIEM due to connectivity issue.
